  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/16a766d4edc058f6fb2089fc4cb2cf79.avif?t=1772537283\" width=1560 height=1040 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/f904662d84bb574f156df9c13b1542d9.avif?t=1772537283\" width=1560 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn ocean garbage into homes, workshops and colorful little gardens.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect floating plastic and driftwood, salvage scraps of the old world, and recycle them into homes that stay afloat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desalinate water, gut fish and board up a shelter to keep everyone safe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your town with plants, refurbished furniture and statues that keep your drifters happy.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/ff960b0b49b44e4273941d60295a2607.poster.avif?t=1772537283\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/ff960b0b49b44e4273941d60295a2607.webm?t=1772537283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/ff960b0b49b44e4273941d60295a2607.mp4?t=1772537283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/8a21d353442f727541b7ebc96dc278e9.avif?t=1772537283\" width=1560 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set sail to explore the flooded world, from soaked ruins to forgotten islands, and discover what still floats beyond the horizon.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore flooded remnants of the old world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescue stranded survivors and friendly animals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Re-discover old technology to improve your town. But be careful your drifters don’t get sick. The old world is polluted!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/d353babc5ad5d67ca357390bd127c707.poster.avif?t=1772537283\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/d353babc5ad5d67ca357390bd127c707.webm?t=1772537283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/d353babc5ad5d67ca357390bd127c707.mp4?t=1772537283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/5dd537caa53686aa9973a1c13fb7ad08.avif?t=1772537283\" width=1560 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your drifters each have their own stories to tell. Recruit specialists who unlock new buildings, quests, and discoveries for your floating community.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find unique drifters like the Birdkeeper, Chemist, and Electrician</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new technologies and story quests through their expertise</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete personal storylines to unlock new mechanics</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/92b7931433b3c0efbb11afe482c167d7.poster.avif?t=1772537283\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/92b7931433b3c0efbb11afe482c167d7.webm?t=1772537283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/92b7931433b3c0efbb11afe482c167d7.mp4?t=1772537283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/23732757365750783c6be85d74ec0118.avif?t=1772537283\" width=1560 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop cleaner, smarter systems that turn waste into progress and keep your floating town thriving in this feel-good apocalypse.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Research new tech to transition from burning firewood to green eel-ectricity generation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build connected production pipelines that turn your floating town into a self-sustaining ecosystem.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean food and develop cures for pollution-born diseases and keep your drifters healthy and productive</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/b11350a3b456d767590fba7f0c880f5a.poster.avif?t=1772537283\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/b11350a3b456d767590fba7f0c880f5a.webm?t=1772537283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/821250/extras/b11350a3b456d767590fba7f0c880f5a.mp4?t=1772537283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
